OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening with some
OL,7,Fpatchy light rain. This clearing
OL,8,Fnortheast overnight to become dry for
OL,9,Fa time. Cloud and more patchy rain
OL,10,Farrive into the west by morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA dry start in the east with
OL,13,Fsome brightness. Cloud and outbreaks
OL,14,Fof rain soon spread east, heavy for a
OL,15,Ftime. This clearing east through the
OL,16,Fevening. Occasionally breezy winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
